column5: All is quite on the western front?
seems like people are fishing elsewhere
The trip I had planed for early June is up in the air as well.
My buddies booked up there for next weekend, at least the place he is going is open for business.
Will be fishing first week of June on the way up to the new Ranch!
Hopefully week after long weekend will be good to go. Anouncement coming by the june 2
